h:100%" border=3D"0" width=3D"60" height=3D"21" alt=3D"y=3Df(x)">
 of <img src=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/images/equations/Jacobian/Inl=
ine2.svg" class=3D"inlineformula" style=3D"max-height:100%;max-width:100%" =
border=3D"0" width=3D"9" height=3D"21" alt=3D"n"> equations in <img src=3D"=
https://mathworld.wolfram.com/images/equations/Jacobian/Inline3.svg" class=
=3D"inlineformula" style=3D"max-height:100%;max-width:100%" border=3D"0" wi=
