/equations/Jacobian/Inline5.svg" class=3D"inlineformula" style=3D"max-heigh=
t:100%;max-width:100%" border=3D"0" width=3D"16" height=3D"21" alt=3D"x_n">=
, written explicitly as
</p>
<div>
